          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer4629355" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15421000074836277634">Generally speaking, we want people&apos;s advantages to be compensated with disadvantages. But what if genetic engineering provided an advantage with no down side? Nancy Kress explores a society in which some people need no sleep (and suffer no side effects) and the &quot;normal&quot; people they live among. A fascinating social study.</span>
  <span id="freeText15421000074836277634" style="display:none">Generally speaking, we want people's advantages to be compensated with disadvantages. But what if genetic engineering provided an advantage with no down side? Nancy Kress explores a society in which some people need no sleep (and suffer no side effects) and the "normal" people they live among. A fascinating social study.</span>
  <a data-text-id="15421000074836277634" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
